episodes.title: LIFE LESSONS LEADING UP TO LEAVING THE TWO BY TWO CULT ❤️
episodes.description:
Hello Everyone! 👋

In 2020 I left a secretive cult I was born and raised! It’s called to outsiders “Two By Twos” and Insiders “The Truth” or “The Way”. 

I got saved in a BIG way by Jesus Christ and his leading me out of deception and spiritual abuse.


Whatever the Holy Spirit wanted me to say in this video, I will trust! One thing I know now, is that God doesn’t expect of me to speak perfectly or sound super intelligent or intellectual to get across what he wants me to convey! I am so thankful for this opportunity to share and however it can benefit someone out there-Glory to God! 🙏✝️❤️
